HEADWORD: Underpossessor
<hw>Un"der*pos*sess`or</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One who
possesses or holds anything subject to the superior of another.</def>
<rj><au>Jer. Taylor.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
